    "Each agent is equipped with unique LLM prompts and role functions tailored to their specific duties within the system.",
    "To accomplish their tasks, agents first convert the received commands to a structured configuration using LLM with the assistance of prompts.",
    "Then the role functions utilize the structured configuration as parameters to process the received data and produce the desired outcomes; see an agent example on the right side of Figure 2.",
    "This workflow endows agents with both language interpretation capabilities and precise execution capabilities.",
